{"tid":687420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］淘寶集運4px唔見左我件貨","createTime":"2018-06-02T08:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T12:35:21.000Z","uid":165886,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b90c88758bf42741e6ecf346c3c53818d3b65b0a","tid":687420,"uid":165886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"比同事老點左我用4px話又平又盛...<br />\n收貨果陣佢地派錯另一個人既件比我<br />\n第二日即刻打電話問我件貨係邊同退番件錯件比佢地<br />\n搞左幾日話搵番我件貨，三四日之內會送到<br />\n由20/5收到電話等好耐都未有消息<br />\n到前幾日再打去，佢又改口風話未知我件貨係邊要再跟進...<br />\n<br />\n想問有人試過咁？可以點做？<br />\n有冇得賠定凍過水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02de363896344c2ccb315c375706484511d2b01","tid":687420,"uid":179477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"你要日日打去追<br />\nCheck過物流訊息未？"},{"pid":"b2521213b68f747c0007d4d330c5004e79759350","tid":687420,"uid":179477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"淘寶嗰邊揀咗延遲收貨先<br />\n真係冇就㩒退錢"},{"pid":"3ad7b880613cb5a6d3455e91c5ad8f765dac1228","tid":687420,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"用過一次  件貨佢話送左比我<br />\n但就係少左一件<br />\n<br />\n之後打去客服佢話派送左啦<br />\n搵唔到WOR<br />\n<br />\n以後BLACKLIST呢間仆街"},{"pid":"2df03e2d8435f84e4b9aeacd62253be792d47794","tid":687420,"uid":89612,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"呢間真係仆街，<br />\n我叫佢送美孚新邨，佢又話個地址唔清楚送唔到，<br />\n打咗幾次電話都話處理緊，件貨係倉度，<br />\n拖咗我成個月，<br />\n後尾查一查佢個倉係邊，我屌你老母，佢個倉係荔枝角　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻打去同佢講，我唔撚洗你搞啦，我自己過嚟倉拎啦<br />\n仆你個臭街，荔枝角送嚟美孚新邨唔撚識送你真係好撚嘢<br />\n之後blacklist咗"},{"pid":"aa239391cbbdb0c482b8e80e3a43b30f51ebc5bf","tid":687420,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"四方狗也不屌<br />\n應該話官方集運 狗也不屌"},{"pid":"28f652ac3258d2dc636a11c6355293583da495fa","tid":687420,"uid":165886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b02de363896344c2ccb315c375706484511d2b01","tid":687420,"uid":179477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"你要日日打去追<br />\nCheck過物流訊息未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:36:11.000Z","msg":"物流信息係我收錯貨之後就冇更新過<br />\n只係顯示「已簽收」...<br />\n退款係只退番集運運費？<br />\n我已經延長左一次，有啲仲過埋期..."},{"pid":"b87af1174697ebcb33783515e6049a53ca4d26cb","tid":687420,"uid":165886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ad7b880613cb5a6d3455e91c5ad8f765dac1228","tid":687420,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"用過一次  件貨佢話送左比我<br />\n但就係少左一件<br />\n<br />\n之後打去客服佢話派送左啦<br />\n搵唔到WOR<br />\n<br />\n以後BLACKLIST呢間仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:37:45.000Z","msg":"真係唔見左我件貨話我知都冇咁嬲<br />\n而家不斷拖唔肯答實要我鳩等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feccb4d39b0d9d8ebca6bbdb6a5ca64171cef6fc","tid":687420,"uid":165886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa239391cbbdb0c482b8e80e3a43b30f51ebc5bf","tid":687420,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"四方狗也不屌<br />\n應該話官方集運 狗也不屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"之前用開sf都好地地，一轉就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f10935427280f5a39f3eebe01fe040f1b69045","tid":687420,"uid":64576,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aa239391cbbdb0c482b8e80e3a43b30f51ebc5bf","tid":687420,"uid":3647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"四方狗也不屌<br />\n應該話官方集運 狗也不屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n順豐好可靠"},{"p