.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5173e5c44e50e6934d89c899846ece061646b6a7","tid":687420,"uid":133277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"用咗多寶幾年 未出過事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d564bd0c328625f48144cd1c5481cc00aa0488f","tid":687420,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"4px咁垃圾都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf6bc52bd2b08e711602b10e1f5dd4f7411638f","tid":687420,"uid":55115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"4px一定要blacklist<br />\n今年年頭訂野，佢老味話執倉又盛扣起我件貨<br />\n日日去買就剩係識話快左快左<br />\n成個幾月先比到件貨我<br />\n間野真係垃圾到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0b526e4e4e841ee915a695d8cfccf35475932d","tid":687420,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"好多年前試過一次，幾日內叫我上佢地office簽左張紙唔追究<br />\n賠足果d. 貨的價錢+集運錢比我就算"},{"pid":"97024c53db4dcaa4a0647b287e42cd7bf9d0474b","tid":687420,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"4px正垃圾<br />\n<br />\n當初見佢話可以送貨去屋企樓下7 仔<br />\n諗住唔駛行咁遠就試吓<br />\n<br />\n點知集運嚟香港時就話送唔到7 仔<br />\n話無位 <br />\n明明就幾件衫2kg都無<br />\n<br />\n搞一輪最後要山長水遠專登去佢上水提貨點攞<br />\n車錢時間都蝕埋"},{"pid":"7b86ce703ed3e58e63eeae60b868f58384a93752","tid":687420,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa5195e4991f060dcf8845f7c5af28a3477dc25c","tid":687420,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e3625dc5f6517cabda26e89ffa5c2cb1fbb1f78","tid":687420,"uid":133365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/032919_1fa60084a787f359fd9d7